            <title>[LU-17087] uninitialized statfs may cause some MDTs never chosen to mkdir</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17087</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On client, the initial statfs to some MDTs may not succeed upon mount (maybe due to network issues), then if the filesystem is imbalanced, those MDTs won&apos;t get chance to be chosen in mkdir.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
